<div style="text-align: left;font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif !important;margin-top: 30px;">
  <p>Dear <%= @policy.primary_user.profile.full_name %></p>
  <p>We hope this email finds you well. We are writing to let you know that your insurance policy, <b><%= @policy.number %></b> has been successfully renewed.
  <p>  Your coverage will continue uninterrupted, and you can rest assured that you and your loved ones are protected.
    We understand how important insurance protection is, and we are glad that we could renew your policy without any hiccups.</p>

  <p>Your policy will now remain in effect until <b><%= @renew_on_date %></b>.</p>

  <p>Please take a moment to review your policy and make sure that it still meets your coverage needs.
    If you have any questions or would like to make any changes, our team of insurance experts is here to help.</p>

  <p>You can reach us at <a href="mailto:<%= t('support_email') %>"><%= t('support_email') %></a>.</p>
  <p>Thank you for choosing us as your insurance provider. We are committed to providing you with the best possible coverage and customer service.</p>
  <p>Best regards, Get Covered</p>
</div>






